# Placeholders are prefixed with $
# Placeholders in brackets [] are optional
#
$type[($scope)][!]: $subject
# - $type: one of [feat|fix|refactor|fmt|test|docs|build|chore]
# - $subject: 1-50 chars, starts lower-case, no trailing dot
# - optional $scope: [A-Za-z0-9/-]+, enclosed in ()
# - optional breaking bang: add ! right after $type or $scope if breaking

[$body]
# - $body: Explain what and why, not how
# - Wrap lines at ~72 chars
# - Use concise lists starting with "-"
# - Reference key files or modules when helpful

[$footers]
# - One trailer per line
# - Wrap lines at ~72 chars
# - If breaking, add a BREAKING CHANGE: footer describing impact/migration
# - Other common trailers: Closes:, Refs: